# NaviWP Release Zip Naming

- When creating a distributable plugin zip for this project, use this exact filename format:
  `naviplus-menu-builder-v<release_number>-<YYYYMMDD>.zip`
- `release_number` must increase sequentially each build (`v5`, `v6`, `v7`, ...), independent of date.
- Use the latest existing build number and increment by 1 for the next package.
- Keep the zip root folder slug as `navi-menu-navigation-builder/` for WordPress.org compatibility.
- Exclude internal/dev files from release zips (for example `golive.md`, `.git*`, `.DS_Store`).
